Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:22.72,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Machina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.51,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Machina, čo sa s tebou deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.15,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Gio, utečte!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.77,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím utečte!
