Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:04:00.91,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie... Ja nie som voľná, ako ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.15,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Machina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.58,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.04,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje, Howling Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.59,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Ten pocit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:46.68,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Machina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.77,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím Liner, nechaj ma ísť!
