Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:05.78,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.39,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj ja budem bojovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechaj tento boj na nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.59,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.68,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som ti, že ťa ochránim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.70,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Obaja ťa Toa ochránime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.53,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin... Gio...
